# for help: "go help {command}" eg "go help mod init"

To start a project:

mkdir $name && cd $name
# create a go.mod file in $PWD with 'go mod init'
go mod init ${module_path} # $module_path typically ends in $name
# edit source code.  For an executable, create package main
# To run the code, 'go run .' or 'go build' to create executable
